{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeListItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeListItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B36ThemeListItemComponentTokensProviderC","title":"OrangeThemeListItemComponentTokensProvider","symbolKind":"class"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of list item","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"list item"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSListItem"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllListItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeListItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"